responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "5E5E2B9242133C822A3818B4BDCC257D", "I jumped as a booming, unfamiliar voice shattered my trance. \"Gods be damned!\" it shouted, sending a flurry of small white birds skyward. From the tone and gruffness, I expected to see a female D\'nir, and my instincts proved correct. She pushed through the copse and emerged on the bank, just beyond where the kirin had stood, arms wide in a gesture of pure exasperation.\"Why\'d you go and do that?\" she demanded, the arch of her brow conveying her dismay. The D\'nir\'s hair, the color of spun gold, was wild, littered with twigs and stray leaves, clearly in need of a brush and oil. Her shorter, feminine beard was far neater, woven into braids with tiny flowers worked into it.")
